{"tid":2025310,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以講下headhunt呢一行？","createTime":"2020-05-20T07:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:42:33.000Z","uid":57036,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d05eac66f28c4bdcbd40793ddf54b888adb7f0","tid":2025310,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"又到轉工旺季<br />\n成日收到d headhunt電話<br />\nchok曬聲咁好關心你<br />\n&ldquo;喂，Peter，最近做野點呀？辛唔辛苦呀？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n作為一條毒撚<br />\n起初聽到都扯扯地<br />\n因為竟然有個陌生人會關心自己<br />\n連自己老死都冇咁好態度<br />\n<br />\n但聽多幾個之後<br />\n法國個個都係清一色呢幾招<br />\n關心完你約你interview<br />\nchok你拎個人資料再拎CV<br />\n然後射JD比你再叫你左in右in<br />\n<br />\n初初真心以為佢地係為你前途著想<br />\n以為佢地好了解行情識好多大粒野<br />\n後尾法國根本就係氹你轉工<br />\n最好兩三個月轉一份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一路都有幾個疑問<br />\n1. 佢地點解會有我個人資料？<br />\n2. 點解佢地咁熟我公司架構，知道唔同職級有咩人？<br />\n3. 介紹到一個candidate有幾多comm？(大概有冇一個range)"},{"pid":"1e9ccdb2c2d11d7506f998609491765f198aaf3e","tid":2025310,"uid":54550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"我淨係知我公司manager grade會用HH<br />\n兩個月人工"},{"pid":"b27f52f0b35d407578df0883553c46cbd7be0bc8","tid":2025310,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e9ccdb2c2d11d7506f998609491765f198aaf3e","tid":2025310,"uid":54550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"我淨係知我公司manager grade會用HH<br />\n兩個月人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"通常底層post就發去公海(eg jobsdb)<br />\n中高層post就靠headhunt搵人內部認購"},{"pid":"ba0a583a63e83e5af377ab8faf65ffb5d80f18dc","tid":2025310,"uid":141863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:22:55.0